Context: The Digital Media and Gaming Incubator is located at 3 Lower Jarvis (second floor) along Toronto's waterfront. It provides affordable space, business and professional services, technology to startups, and encourages exploration, discoveries, and collaboration. Interested individuals can contact incubator@georgebrown.ca for information about office spaces or hotdesks. The phone numbers for inquiries are 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559, and email is ask.george@georgebrown.ca. For college news, upcoming events, tours, and application deadlines, individuals can sign up on the website. The Incubator shares space with the School of Design. The information on the website is subject to change without notice and should not be viewed as a representation, offer, or warranty. Contact George Brown College for fee requirements.
